{
  "stem": "16163.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So here I was without a jacket and a dress with holes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And that's how I got out of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Same type-- we all had the same type of-- like we would say in Jewish, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And torn and dirty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rags.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not uniforms--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From other-- most likely from other prisoners.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The clothes, which was very old already or used by some and taken off when they were gassed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How we looked?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I felt we all look like alike.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all looked alike.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I was-- when I got to, to Auschwitz into the sauna there-- what I called a sauna-- there were people who I knew.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once the hair was off, you didn't know people anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You didn't even-- maybe recognize them by their eyes, but that's all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not that I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just the head and every other hair.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, underneath the arms and the rest of the body hair.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If there was, I, I didn't notice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll be honest.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sure that was going on, but I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that particular--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--time, all you thought of, what's next?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The barracks were wooden barracks with a roof.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you went in, and there was like in the middle of the barrack-- I believe they must have been horse barracks at one time, you know, like for horses and animals?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the middle was like a walkway, a higher walkway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's where the SS come back and forth on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On each side of them were what we called [? coverlets, ?] which-- the bunk beds, right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were five on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Five levels?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Five levels.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
